Package prefs.editors

Class Summary
VSAbstractBetterEditor The class VSAbstractBetterEditor, is an improved VSAbstractEditor.
VSAbstractEditor The class VSAbstractEditor, an object of this class is used in order to edit a VSPrefs object.
VSColorChooser The class VSColorChooser, is for selecting a color within an editor.
VSEditorFrame The class VSEditorFrame, this is a wrapper around an VSAbstractEditor object, which should be displayed in its own frame.
VSEditorTable The class VSEditorTable, each VSAbstractEditor uses an object of this class for displaying all editable items!
VSProcessEditor The class VSProcessEditor, is for editing a VSInternalProcess object.
VSSimulatorEditor The class VSSimulatorEditor, is for editing a VSSimulator object.
